## 🔍 6. SEO Implementation Checklist
- [ ] **Keyword Density:** Embed the primary keyword in the H1 title, intro paragraph, one H2 heading, and the FAQ.
- [ ] **Slug Formatting:** Use lowercase, hyphenated slugs containing the target brand and year (e.g. `chandigarh-university-online-mba-review-2026`).
- [ ] **Internal Interlinking:** Link to at least 2 other related review articles on the portal.
- [ ] **External Links:** Always point official university references directly to their official `.edu.in` or primary domains.
